#: strategies-new-concept-adapting-language_en.txt:2
msgid "Adapting language"
msgstr ""

#: strategies-new-concept-adapting-language_en.txt:4
msgid ""
"C2_Can adapt the language of a very wide range of texts in order to present "
"the main content in a register and degree of sophistication and detail "
"appropriate to the audience concerned."
msgstr ""

#: strategies-new-concept-adapting-language_en.txt:8
msgid ""
"C1_Can explain technical terminology and difficult concepts when "
"communicating with non-experts about matters within their own field of "
"specialisation."
"Can adapt their language (e.g. syntax, idiomaticity, jargon) in order to "
"make a complex specialist topic accessible to recipients who are not "
"familiar with it."
"Can paraphrase and interpret complex, technical texts, using suitably non-"
"technical language for a recipient who does not have specialist knowledge."
msgstr ""

#: strategies-new-concept-adapting-language_en.txt:11
msgid ""
"B2+_Can explain technical topics within their field, using suitably non-"
"technical language for a recipient who does not have specialist knowledge."
"Can make a specific, complex piece of information in their field clearer and "
"more explicit for others by paraphrasing it in simpler language."
msgstr ""

#: strategies-new-concept-adapting-language_en.txt:13
msgid ""
"B2_Can make accessible for others the main contents of a text on a subject "
"of interest (e.g. an essay, a forum discussion, a presentation) by "
"paraphrasing in simpler language."
msgstr ""

#: strategies-new-concept-adapting-language_en.txt:15
msgid ""
"B1+_Can paraphrase more simply the main points made in short, "
"straightforward texts on familiar subjects (e.g. short magazine articles, "
"interviews) to make the contents accessible for others."
msgstr ""

#: strategies-new-concept-adapting-language_en.txt:17
msgid ""
"B1_Can paraphrase short passages in a simple fashion, using the original "
"order of the text."
msgstr ""

#: strategies-new-concept-adapting-language_en.txt:19
msgid ""
"A2_Can repeat the main point of a simple message on an everyday subject, "
"using different formulation to help someone else understand it."
msgstr ""

